  "variant": "PWSPEC-NB V2 -- 4 PRODUCER warps + 4 CONSUMER warps (256 thd/CTA). Named bar.arrive (non-blocking) + bar.sync (blocking) with rotating bar indices per slot. bar 1=slot 0 ready, bar 2=slot 0 consumed, bar 3=slot 1 ready, bar 4=slot 1 consumed. Each bar count=256 (full CTA). Per consumer: 1 M-sub (16M) x 8 N-sub-8 = 8 mma.m16n8k16, 32 f32 acc/lane (back to N107 reg pressure, NOT N127's 64). Producer races ahead via bar.arrive; consumer races ahead via bar.arrive on consumed signal.",
